---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const CONTACT_LINK = "mailto:gauthamail@gmail.com";
---

<BaseLayout title="CV" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <!-- HEADER -->
  <section class="mt-2">
    <div class="text-3xl w-full font-bold">CV</div>

    <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
      <p class="text-lg">
        I’m a founder–operator who has spent the last 15+ years building, running, and learning from
        internet-first businesses — across education, software, and consulting.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg">
        This is a short, honest snapshot of what I’ve done, what I’m doing now, and what I’m good at.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CURRENT -->
  <section class="mt-12">
    <div class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">What I’m doing now</div>

    <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg list-disc pl-6">
      <li>
        Running <b>The Second Design</b>, an education design studio focused on cohort-based learning,
        curriculum design, and training educators to build effective learning environments.
      </li>
      <li>
        Building and operating <b>SellOnTube</b>, a YouTube-first customer acquisition system for internet businesses.
      </li>
      <li>
        Running <b>Turpentine Academy</b>, where I turn real business learning into practical workshops and playbooks.
      </li>
      <li>
        Working on a <b>US healthcare nurse scheduling product</b> — a long-term SaaS bet focused on operations and burnout reduction.
      </li>
      <li>
        Consulting with founders to help them cut through noise, find the real bottleneck, and execute with clarity.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- EXPERIENCE -->
  <section class="mt-12">
    <div class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Experience</div>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg">
      <div>
        <div class="font-semibold">The Second Design</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Founder — 2021 to present</div>
        <p class="mt-1">
          Built and operated an education design studio working with students, professionals, and organisations to design
          high-quality learning experiences — including curriculum design, learning cadence, and facilitator training.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="font-semibold">VC-backed Education Company</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Founder / Operator — ~8 years</div>
        <p class="mt-1">
          Built and ran a venture-backed education company in India. Designed programs, built teams,
          scaled operations, and worked closely with students, professionals, and partners.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="font-semibold">Startup Village Collective / Pupilfirst</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Co-founder / Early Operator</div>
        <p class="mt-1">
          Worked on early-stage founder education and incubation. Helped students and professionals
          learn by building real products, not just studying theory.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SKILLS -->
  <section class="mt-12">
    <div class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">What I’m good at</div>

    <ul class="space-y-2 text-lg list-disc pl-6">
      <li>Breaking complex problems into clear, actionable plans</li>
      <li>Product thinking and product–market fit diagnosis</li>
      <li>Go-to-market strategy for internet-first businesses</li>
      <li>Education design: curriculum, cohorts, learning cadence</li>
      <li>Founder operating systems, delegation, and leverage</li>
      <li>Writing and teaching to clarify thinking</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTEXT -->
  <section class="mt-12">
    <div class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Context & constraints</div>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-lg">
      <p>
        I’ve worked across <b>VC-backed</b> and <b>bootstrapped</b> environments, with teams both large and small,
        across India and the US market.
      </p>
      <p>
        I don’t claim deep domain expertise in every industry. Where I add value is in the
        <b>horizontal skills</b> that cut across businesses: clarity, execution, positioning, and systems.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="mt-12">
    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 p-6">
      <div class="text-xl font-bold">Want to work together?</div>
      <p class="mt-2 text-lg">
        If you’re building something internet-first and feel stuck or overwhelmed,
        I’m happy to take a look.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-5">
        <a class="btn" href={CONTACT_LINK}>Email me</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>